FBIS4-46124 "jptot022__l94033" JPRS-TOT-94-022-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 21 May 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA REGIONAL AFFAIRS IDF Seizes `Terrorist' Leader al-Dirani; Hizballah Reaction IDF Seizes `Terrorist' Leader al-Dirani; Hizballah Reaction Al-Musawi Says No to `Bargaining' NC2105092294 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0900 GMT 21 May 94 NC2105092294 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] In a statement to REUTER today, Husayn al-Musawi, a Hizballah leader, confirmed the report on the abduction of al-Haj Mustafa al-Dirani. He said that this Israeli operation is part of the ongoing fighting between Hizballah and Israel. Al-Musawi added that Israel wants to use al-Dirani as a bargaining chip to insure the release of navigator Ron Arad. But this Israeli attempt will not succeed, he added.
